				<div class="hvres-meaning">Âm Pinyin: <a href="/py/ge2">gé <span class="small gray han">ㄍㄜˊ</span></a>, <a href="/py/he2">hé <span class="small gray han">ㄏㄜˊ</span></a><br/>Âm Nôm: <a href="/nom/các">các</a><br/>Âm Nhật (onyomi): <a href="/reading/1/1/コウ">コウ (kō)</a><br/>Âm Nhật (kunyomi): <a href="/reading/1/2/くぐりど">くぐりど (kugurido)</a><br/>Âm Hàn: <a href="/reading/1/3/합">합</a><br/>Âm Quảng Đông: <a href="/reading/1/4/gap3">gap3</a>, <a href="/reading/1/4/gok3">gok3</a>, <a href="/reading/1/4/hap6">hap6</a></div><p class="hvres-source">Tự hình <span class="badge">2</span></p>
